            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h1><b>Cross-border Pension</b></h1>
                <br />


                <p class="well-lg">
                    <h5>
                        This product enables expatriate employees in companies registered in Nigeria and Nigerian citizens working in other countries to participate in the Nigerian Contributory Pension scheme.
                    </h5>
                        <br />
                    <br />
                    <ul>
                        <h5>
                            <li><b>Any foreign employee in Nigeria can join the scheme at his/her discretion.</b></li>
                            <li><b>The RSA opened shall be denominated in Naira. </b> </li>
                            <li><b>In the event of permanent relocation, the individual shall give 3 months prior notice to the PFA before exiting the scheme. </b></li>
                            <li><b>Nigerians working abroad are allowed to join the scheme by making voluntary contributions.</b></li>
                        </h5>
                    </ul>
                   
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>
</section>